nergy\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all I can do at this point.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Make 2026 the year of working smarter \\\"Once you are in that race [the final], anything can happen.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2723}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an open race, once we get on the start line, it's open.\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an open race\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just need to go into that race headstrong and perform my best.\\\"\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 3023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that race headstrong\", \"from\"